title: Gloryhammer - Space 1992-Rise of the Chaos Wizards(LE 2CD)2015
description:
Space 1992: Rise of the Chaos Wizards is the second album by Scottish-Swiss symphonic power metal band Gloryhammer. It was released on September 25, 2015. The deluxe edition contains an additional disc of orchestral renditions of the full album, with alternate titles.
